you're doing. Go to bed with him.

01:13:00.367 --> 01:13:04.235
- That's not fair.
- Yeah, a lot of things aren't fair.

01:13:06.789 --> 01:13:09.957
Lucas, you and I were just friends.

01:13:14.004 --> 01:13:15.547
Why?

01:13:16.299 --> 01:13:20.083
