CAPPIE: You gotta get out of here.
- Come on!

01:23:28.241 --> 01:23:31.363
- Get him out of here!
- No way!

01:23:31.538 --> 01:23:35.404
- I'm staying in!
- Get him out of there! Time!

01:23:36.083 --> 01:23:39.415
- Coach, got no time-outs left!
